request.description:
### Get Propuesta by ID

This endpoint retrieves a specific proposal by its ID.

#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object representing the proposal. Below is a JSON schema representing the structure of the response:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "description": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "created_at": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    },
    "updated_at": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    }
  }
}

 ```

